PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JORDAN LIVINGSTON, of Hamilton, Ontario, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Flavia E. Redelmeier, whose term has expired.
